NOTE ON THE SOURCE NOVEL (重要：原著著作權聲明)

This game is a fan adaptation inspired by the web novel
《凡人修仙傳》 by 忘語 (Wang Yu). The MIT License above covers ONLY this
project's source code, tooling, and the original transformative story-summary
data authored for this game. It does NOT grant any rights to 《凡人修仙傳》
itself. All rights to the novel — its full text and original expression —
remain with 忘語 and the respective rights holders. This repository contains
NO verbatim text of the novel. This is a non-commercial fan work; if the
rights holders object, the corresponding content will be removed on request.
